3
00:00:16,824 --> 00:00:18,494
<font color="yellow">Is this where you live, Dong Hui?</font>

4
00:00:19,558 --> 00:00:20,558
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

5
00:00:21,318 --> 00:00:23,688
<font color="yellow">I never knew there was such a shabby town in Seoul.</font>

6
00:00:24,558 --> 00:00:25,758
<font color="yellow">It's creepy.</font>

7
00:00:27,888 --> 00:00:28,958
<font color="yellow">Mi Joo.</font>

8
00:00:30,558 --> 00:00:33,818
<font color="yellow">Well... I'll get going, then.</font>

9
00:00:44,758 --> 00:00:45,918
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

10
00:00:48,758 --> 00:00:50,318
<font color="yellow">See you, Dong Hui.</font>

11
00:01:30,918 --> 00:01:32,618
<font color="yellow">Why do you look so anxious?</font>

12
00:01:34,488 --> 00:01:35,558
<font color="yellow">I'm fine.</font>

13
00:01:36,218 --> 00:01:38,088
<font color="yellow">You're strange today.</font>

14
00:01:38,618 --> 00:01:42,088
<font color="yellow">By the way, I can't believe that Dong Hui lives in such town.</font>

15
00:01:42,318 --> 00:01:44,258
<font color="yellow">I can't never live there even if I get paid.</font>

16
00:01:45,958 --> 00:01:48,958
<font color="yellow">It was shocking to find out such a backward region in this city.</font>

17
00:01:49,958 --> 00:01:51,158
<font color="yellow">Why don't they redevelop the town?</font>

18
00:01:51,618 --> 00:01:55,258
<font color="yellow">They should bulldoze out and rebuild a new town to make Seoul clean,</font>

19
00:01:55,558 --> 00:01:56,588
<font color="yellow">right?</font>

20
00:01:56,958 --> 00:01:59,158
<font color="yellow">It was so spooky.</font>

21
00:01:59,588 --> 00:02:01,558
<font color="yellow">I thought it was a shooting place.</font>

22
00:02:02,288 --> 00:02:05,318
<font color="yellow">Let's shoot our dramas in that neighborhood.</font>

23
00:02:06,558 --> 00:02:08,558
<font color="yellow">I guess we have found a good location today.</font>

24
00:02:09,128 --> 00:02:10,258
<font color="yellow">Please stop.</font>

25
00:02:11,988 --> 00:02:13,018
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

26
00:02:13,658 --> 00:02:15,058
<font color="yellow">What's the matter with you?</font>

27
00:02:15,058 --> 00:02:16,588
<font color="yellow">Please stop it already!</font>

28
00:02:19,858 --> 00:02:22,358
<font color="yellow">What's wrong? What makes you burst out?</font>

29
00:02:22,358 --> 00:02:23,628
<font color="yellow">It's your attitude.</font>

30
00:02:23,688 --> 00:02:24,788
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with my attitude?</font>

31
00:02:24,788 --> 00:02:27,518
<font color="yellow">How could you say that in front of her?</font>

32
00:02:27,758 --> 00:02:29,858
<font color="yellow">I just said the town she lives in is creepy,</font>

33
00:02:30,058 --> 00:02:32,128
<font color="yellow">not herself.</font>

34
00:02:32,358 --> 00:02:34,858
<font color="yellow">You may not know, but not only in Seoul,</font>

35
00:02:35,288 --> 00:02:38,288
<font color="yellow">but also in Korea, many people still live in places like that.</font>

36
00:02:44,818 --> 00:02:46,518
<font color="yellow">(Ms. Oh Dong Hui)</font>

37
00:02:54,158 --> 00:02:56,158
<font color="yellow">(Mr. Seo Cheol Min)</font>

38
00:03:09,388 --> 00:03:10,988
<font color="yellow">What's gotten into you all of a sudden?</font>

39
00:03:11,318 --> 00:03:12,758
<font color="yellow">Did I do anything wrong?</font>

40
00:03:12,818 --> 00:03:14,588
<font color="yellow">We all live in a different circumstance.</font>

41
00:03:14,618 --> 00:03:16,518
<font color="yellow">Why do you never bother to care about others' feelings?</font>

42
00:03:17,888 --> 00:03:19,618
<font color="yellow">That's ridiculous, Seong Joon.</font>

43
00:03:20,418 --> 00:03:22,888
<font color="yellow">So you want me to care about her feelings?</font>

44
00:03:23,388 --> 00:03:26,258
<font color="yellow">Are you taking on Dong Hui's side in front of me?</font>

45
00:03:26,788 --> 00:03:29,258
<font color="yellow">Did you just say I should care about how she'd feel?</font>

46
00:03:29,588 --> 00:03:32,718
<font color="yellow">I didn't mean to offend her. The building was too old,</font>

47
00:03:32,758 --> 00:03:34,818
<font color="yellow">so I just said what I felt.</font>

48
00:03:35,218 --> 00:03:36,558
<font color="yellow">Am I wrong?</font>

49
00:03:36,558 --> 00:03:38,918
<font color="yellow">Whether you're right or wrong, that doesn't matter at all.</font>

50
00:03:38,988 --> 00:03:41,018
<font color="yellow">You should think how others would feel before you speak.</font>

51
00:03:41,888 --> 00:03:44,118
<font color="yellow">That's their one and only home.</font>

52
00:03:44,188 --> 00:03:46,518
<font color="yellow">Do you know how terrible it sounded...</font>

53
00:03:47,358 --> 00:03:49,918
<font color="yellow">when you said it should be bulldozed out?</font>

54
00:03:49,958 --> 00:03:50,988
<font color="yellow">So what?</font>

55
00:03:51,118 --> 00:03:53,518
<font color="yellow">Are you saying I should apologize to Dong Hui...</font>

56
00:03:53,558 --> 00:03:55,488
<font color="yellow">for despising her place?</font>

57
00:03:55,488 --> 00:03:56,558
<font color="yellow">Mi Joo!</font>

58
00:03:58,018 --> 00:04:00,188
<font color="yellow">Fine, I am sorry. That was too much.</font>

59
00:04:00,388 --> 00:04:02,318
<font color="yellow">I know you hate when I'm being rude,</font>

60
00:04:02,658 --> 00:04:04,458
<font color="yellow">but I've become sensitive because of my dad.</font>

61
00:04:12,988 --> 00:04:15,518
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon!</font>

62
00:05:03,958 --> 00:05:06,158
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui, please answer the phone.</font>

63
00:05:10,018 --> 00:05:12,118
<font color="yellow">(Director Han)</font>

64
00:05:33,288 --> 00:05:35,158
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui. Dong Hui.</font>

65
00:05:40,958 --> 00:05:43,888
<font color="yellow">(Director Han)</font>

66
00:05:54,918 --> 00:05:55,988
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

67
00:05:57,188 --> 00:05:58,188
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

68
00:06:10,818 --> 00:06:11,958
<font color="yellow">Please go to Bangbae-dong.</font>

69
00:06:15,288 --> 00:06:17,018
<font color="yellow">The number you have dialed is not in service.</font>

70
00:06:34,958 --> 00:06:36,658
<font color="yellow">(Director Han)</font>

71
00:06:36,658 --> 00:06:38,058
<font color="yellow">(10 missed calls)</font>

