00:07:13,758 --> 00:07:15,958
<font color="yellow">(9.70 dollars)</font>

74
00:07:23,958 --> 00:07:26,818
<font color="yellow">I am sorry, but I will get off here. I am sorry.</font>

75
00:08:19,858 --> 00:08:21,988
<font color="yellow">Wait, can you stop the car?</font>

76
00:08:41,858 --> 00:08:43,458
<font color="yellow">(Director Han)</font>

77
00:08:43,458 --> 00:08:44,528
<font color="yellow">(11 missed calls)</font>

78
00:09:11,528 --> 00:09:12,888
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you picking up my calls?</font>

79
00:09:14,488 --> 00:09:16,088
<font color="yellow">Why won't you pick up my calls?</font>

80
00:09:17,788 --> 00:09:20,988
<font color="yellow">Do I have to take your calls?</font>

81
00:09:24,758 --> 00:09:26,988
<font color="yellow">I was worried. You made me worried.</font>

82
00:09:28,158 --> 00:09:30,758
<font color="yellow">Why don't you listen to me? Why won't you pick up the phone?</font>

83
00:09:32,918 --> 00:09:34,158
<font color="yellow">It's funny.</font>

84
00:09:34,918 --> 00:09:35,918
<font color="yellow">Isn't it?</font>

85
00:09:39,618 --> 00:09:42,188
<font color="yellow">Why would you be worried about me?</font>

86
00:09:42,371 --> 00:09:44,031
<font color="yellow">You could have just said that you live in Bangbae-dong.</font>

87
00:09:44,258 --> 00:09:46,388
<font color="yellow">Our house is not the only house in Bangbae-dong, is it?</font>

88
00:09:46,418 --> 00:09:48,618
<font color="yellow">But we couldn't get off together.</font>

89
00:09:48,758 --> 00:09:50,958
<font color="yellow">We can't say that we live in the same town.</font>

90
00:09:51,858 --> 00:09:52,918
<font color="yellow">I already know...</font>

91
00:09:53,658 --> 00:09:57,588
<font color="yellow">that I put you in a difficult situation at work.</font>

92
00:09:59,088 --> 00:10:00,618
<font color="yellow">So how could I?</font>

93
00:11:04,888 --> 00:11:06,388
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

94
00:11:10,358 --> 00:11:11,818
<font color="yellow">You must be crazy.</font>

95
00:11:13,688 --> 00:11:15,288
<font color="yellow">Do you think you are the only one who drank?</font>

96
00:11:15,818 --> 00:11:17,288
<font color="yellow">I drank, too.</font>

97
00:11:17,888 --> 00:11:20,188
<font color="yellow">Do you think you're the only one who's drunk? I'm drunk, too.</font>

98
00:11:21,218 --> 00:11:22,258
<font color="yellow">But still...</font>

99
00:11:25,288 --> 00:11:26,788
<font color="yellow">What am I suppose to do?</font>

100
00:11:50,458 --> 00:11:52,658
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui. Dong Hui.</font>

101
00:13:14,418 --> 00:13:16,918
<font color="yellow">- Let go of me! - Let go!</font>

102
00:13:16,918 --> 00:13:17,918
<font color="yellow">Let go!</font>

103
00:13:19,518 --> 00:13:21,288
<font color="yellow">You can't do this.</font>

104
00:13:21,458 --> 00:13:23,588
<font color="yellow">You can't do this to us.</font>

105
00:13:23,778 --> 00:13:26,308
<font color="yellow">I gave my everything to this store.</font>

106
00:13:26,848 --> 00:13:30,148
<font color="yellow">I came here day and night for the past 30 years.</font>

107
00:13:30,318 --> 00:13:32,848
<font color="yellow">I spent all my youth working here.</font>

108
00:13:38,348 --> 00:13:39,718
<font color="yellow">You sold this building, didn't you?</font>

109
00:13:40,288 --> 00:13:41,518
<font color="yellow">Where's the building owner?</font>

110
00:13:41,848 --> 00:13:44,948
<font color="yellow">Let me meet the owner. You know who it is.</font>

111
00:13:45,048 --> 00:13:46,418
<font color="yellow">Let go of me.</font>

112
00:13:46,588 --> 00:13:50,718
<font color="yellow">You should've left when I offered to pay. Why are you doing this now?</font>

113
00:13:50,788 --> 00:13:54,118
<font color="yellow">This is wrong. You can't do this to me.</font>

114
00:13:54,148 --> 00:13:57,688
<font color="yellow">I've been a good person all my life.</font>

115
00:13:59,688 --> 00:14:02,518
<font color="yellow">- Oh, dear. - What's happening to our town?</font>

116
00:14:02,518 --> 00:14:04,018
<font color="yellow">It's so unsettling.</font>

117
00:14:04,048 --> 00:14:06,718
<font color="yellow">I heard that someone is buying up the buildings here.</font>

118
00:14:06,748 --> 00:14:08,388
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

119
00:14:08,718 --> 00:14:11,518
<font color="yellow">Hey, you must know everything. Who will be the next?</font>

120
00:14:11,518 --> 00:14:14,218
<font color="yellow">You should share such information with neighbors.</font>

121
00:14:16,188 --> 00:14:17,218
<font color="yellow">Stop right there.</font>

122
00:14:18,818 --> 00:14:21,018
<font color="yellow">It's your uncle who bought my building, right?</font>

123
00:14:21,148 --> 00:14:23,988
<font color="yellow">Where is he? Tell me where he is now!</font>

124
00:14:23,988 --> 00:14:26,988
<font color="yellow">What are you doing? Please calm down.</font>

125
00:14:27,288 --> 00:14:30,618
<font color="yellow">I need to see him right now. I can't move out like this.</font>

126
00:14:31,518 --> 00:14:33,518
<font color="yellow">I can't reach him right now.</font>

127
00:14:33,788 --> 00:14:35,688
<font color="yellow">I don't get to meet him these days.</font>

128
00:14:35,718 --> 00:14:37,048
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

129
00:14:37,048 --> 00:14:39,418
<font color="yellow">So your uncle is the owner of this building?</font>

130
00:14:40,018 --> 00:14:41,618
<font color="yellow">Didn't you just hear him?</font>

131
00:14:41,618 --> 00:14:44,088
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, you can't do this here.</font>

132
00:14:44,388 --> 00:14:45,848
<font color="yellow">Bring him here!</font>

133
00:14:46,018 --> 00:14:48,448
<font color="yellow">Tell him to come here right now.</font>

134
00:14:49,488 --> 00:14:51,418
<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee, are you all right?</font>

135
00:14:52,818 --> 00:14:54,288
<font color="yellow">Are you out of mind? Come here.</font>

136
00:14:54,288 --> 00:14:56,348
<font color="yellow">- I said stop it. - Get off. Let go of me.</font>

137
00:14:56,548 --> 00:14:59,118
<font color="yellow">Do you want to see me die here?</font>

138
00:15:01,288 --> 00:15:03,918
<font color="yellow">Go find him right now.</font>

139
00:15:03,918 --> 00:15:06,418
<font color="yellow">Bring your uncle here now.</font>

140
00:15:06,548 --> 00:15:08,448
<font color="yellow">This is so unfair.</font>

141
00:15:08,448 --> 00:15:10,988
<font color="yellow">I can't live like this.</font>

142
00:15:12,348 --> 00:15:15,988
<font color="yellow">We didn't steal anything. It wasn't us!</font>

143
00:15:16,018 --> 00:15:17,948
<font color="yellow">How dare you lie to me?</font>

144
00:15:18,118 --> 00:15:20,588
<font color="yellow">What's that snack your brother is holding, then?</font>

145
00:15:21,288 --> 00:15:22,788
<font color="yellow">Stop crying!</font>

146
00:15:22,818 --> 00:15:24,218
<font color="yellow">Don't hit my brother.</font>

147
00:15:24,548 --> 00:15:26,918
<font color="yellow">My brother didn't steal it.</font>

148
00:15:27,518 --> 00:15:29,918
<font color="yellow">A passer-by gave this to him!</font>

149
00:15:29,918 --> 00:15:32,318
<font color="yellow">Who on earth would give snacks to kids like you?</font>

150
00:15:32,888 --> 00:15:36,018
<font color="yellow">I can't let it slide. You're just like your father.</font>

151
00:15:36,418 --> 00:15:38,418
<font color="yellow">I'll teach you some lessons today.</font>

152
00:15:39,118 --> 00:15:40,188
<font color="yellow">Come here.</font>

153
00:15:50,618 --> 00:15:53,218
<font color="yellow">Go find him right now.</font>

154
00:15:53,218 --> 00:15:55,718
<font color="yellow">Bring your uncle here now.</font>

155
00:15:55,888 --> 00:16:00,218
<font color="yellow">This is nonsense. I'm going to die.</font>

156
00:16:12,748 --> 00:16:13,748
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

157
00:16:17,318 --> 00:16:19,588
<font color="yellow">Did you think I wouldn't be able to find you?</font>

158
00:16:24,088 --> 00:16:25,888
<font color="yellow">Can you see me?</font>

159
00:16:26,948 --> 00:16:28,388
<font color="yellow">I'm looking at you right now.</font>

160
00:16:33,948 --> 00:16:35,718
<font color="yellow">I guess you have shame at least.</font>

161
00:16:36,218 --> 00:16:37,588
<font color="yellow">You ran away...</font>

162
00:16:38,388 --> 00:16:41,148
<font color="yellow">and even hid when you saw me.</font>

163
00:16:41,588 --> 00:16:45,088
<font color="yellow">I am sorry. I drank too much that day.</font>

164
00:16:46,088 --> 00:16:48,418
<font color="yellow">I knew what kind of person you were,</font>

165
00:16:48,648 --> 00:16:49,988
<font color="yellow">so it's not surprising at all.</font>

166
00:16:50,448 --> 00:16:51,618
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

167
00:16:51,718 --> 00:16:53,948
<font color="yellow">I don't know what's wrong with me, either.</font>

168
00:16:54,218 --> 00:16:56,618
<font color="yellow">I'm really doing my best...</font>

169
00:16:56,618 --> 00:16:59,088
<font color="yellow">to be girlish and modest.</font>

170
00:16:59,888 --> 00:17:01,788
<font color="yellow">What did you just say?</font>

171
00:17:02,348 --> 00:17:03,418
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

172
00:17:04,118 --> 00:17:05,948
<font color="yellow">it seems impossible.</font>

173
00:17:06,218 --> 00:17:07,988
<font color="yellow">I've tried in my entire life,</font>

174
00:17:08,218 --> 00:17:11,088
<font color="yellow">but I always end up like that.</font>

175
00:17:11,618 --> 00:17:13,658
<font color="yellow">I'm really bad at romance.</font>

176
00:17:13,658 --> 00:17:15,418
<font color="yellow">The beginning may be romantic,</font>

177
00:17:15,988 --> 00:17:19,118
<font color="yellow">but it turns out to be comedy or horror.</font>

178
00:17:21,318 --> 00:17:22,658
<font color="yellow">Speaking of it,</font>

179
00:17:23,818 --> 00:17:25,848
<font color="yellow">on that night...</font>

180
00:17:26,818 --> 00:17:27,918
<font color="yellow">What about that night?</font>

181
00:17:28,388 --> 00:17:29,418
<font color="yellow">Did you do anything...</font>

182
00:17:29,948 --> 00:17:31,918
<font color="yellow">to me by any chance?</font>

183
00:17:31,918 --> 00:17:33,188
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

184
00:17:33,618 --> 00:17:36,448
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry. I did it again.</font>

185
00:17:36,488 --> 00:17:39,658
<font color="yellow">I always try not to speak what's on my mind,</font>

186
00:17:39,948 --> 00:17:41,918
<font color="yellow">but I speak it out in spite of myself.</font>

187
00:17:45,718 --> 00:17:46,888
<font color="yellow">You're bleeding!</font>

188
00:17:49,288 --> 00:17:52,218
<font color="yellow">You should work in the office.</font>

189
00:17:52,218 --> 00:17:55,818
<font color="yellow">You got hurt because you're working at a construction site.</font>

190
00:17:55,918 --> 00:17:57,818
<font color="yellow">- I can do it myself. - Stay still.</font>

191
00:17:58,158 --> 00:18:00,588
<font color="yellow">If you don't treat it now, it'll leave a big scar.</font>

192
00:18:04,918 --> 00:18:06,518
<font color="yellow">So why did you...</font>

193
00:18:06,658 --> 00:18:08,688
<font color="yellow">make such reckless investment?</font>

194
00:18:09,018 --> 00:18:12,848
<font color="yellow">I can't believe you bankrupted that big company.</font>

195
00:18:12,848 --> 00:18:14,218
<font color="yellow">Look how you ended up now.</font>

196
00:18:15,118 --> 00:18:18,288
<font color="yellow">Right, I promised you not to mention your company.</font>

197
00:18:18,948 --> 00:18:20,048
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

198
00:18:24,463 --> 00:18:26,233
<font color="yellow">Gosh, it must hurt a lot.</font>

199
00:18:43,301 --> 00:18:44,301
<font color="yellow">Did you have lunch?</font>

200
00:18:45,518 --> 00:18:46,548
<font color="yellow">Sorry?</font>

201
00:18:49,788 --> 00:18:51,118
<font color="yellow">All I have is ramyeon.</font>

202
00:18:53,888 --> 00:18:57,448
<font color="yellow">My goodness. This isn't a place where a person lives.</font>

203
00:18:57,518 --> 00:18:59,388
<font color="yellow">Look, there's nothing in your fridge.</font>

204
00:18:59,818 --> 00:19:02,588
<font color="yellow">I'd better bring my aunt's kimchi here.</font>

205
00:19:05,518 --> 00:19:07,818
<font color="yellow">Stop. Let me do it.</font>

206
00:19:08,518 --> 00:19:10,158
<font color="yellow">I'm good at making ramyeon.</font>

207
00:19:29,288 --> 00:19:30,448
<font color="yellow">Hyun Woo!</font>

208
00:19:31,048 --> 00:19:33,218
<font color="yellow">It's ready. Come eat some.</font>

209
00:19:40,218 --> 00:19:41,588
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

210
00:19:43,718 --> 00:19:46,848
<font color="yellow">You want 50 percent of the profit of my cafe?</font>

